msgid "|image775|"
msgstr "|image775|"

#: ../../source/serials.rst:544
msgid ""
"Another option is to click the 'Renew' link to the right of the subscription "
"on the Serial Collection page."
msgstr "另個選項是按期刊館藏頁面訂閱右方的 '續訂' 連結。"

